<normalizedToken id="F834FC9BB4D22D434BCC3D603ADB18BF" originalValue="Gewöhnliches" pageId="null" pageNumber="483">Gewoehnliches</normalizedToken>
Sonnengold
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
</title>
<subSubSection id="40ED79AE82FDB8D79F9EBA0D02E91828" pageId="null" pageNumber="483" type="description">
<paragraph id="55202BECFCEB631686B5A66EACCF814F" pageId="null" pageNumber="483">
5-50 cm hoch, 
<normalizedToken id="5E294A96DA83A1FB5A0FFEC3CF534DB1" originalValue="würzig" pageId="null" pageNumber="483">wuerzig</normalizedToken>
riechend. Stengel am Grunde verzweigt, 
<emphasis id="06728A8638B65C4411C233C0A91542FE" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="483">verholzt.</emphasis>
<normalizedToken id="7FC3FB1F00A8461D88EF628B87A9E6BC" originalValue="Blätter" pageId="null" pageNumber="483">Blaetter</normalizedToken>
schmal lanzettlich, 
<emphasis id="72ED16332D5B68D145F0D6F08D5903F1" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="483">am Rande nach unten eingerollt.</emphasis>
<normalizedToken id="CE5BBCF0BC5F818968C3D204AF8CFBD6" originalValue="Blütenköpfe" pageId="null" pageNumber="483">Bluetenkoepfe</normalizedToken>
kurz gestielt. 
<emphasis id="EC103E476B37AF38D902D5D0314B6AFC" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="483">
<normalizedToken id="3316ED622079FC2CEBF484B12E68C45A" originalValue="Hülle" pageId="null" pageNumber="483">Huelle</normalizedToken>
halbkugelig, 4
</emphasis>
- 
<emphasis id="2B80410E04D3ABFC8272797405276432" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="483">
6 mm lang und ebenso dick. 
<normalizedToken id="F761EF40DD83DABB0DC15B7D8D8644C7" originalValue="Hüllblätter" pageId="null" pageNumber="483">Huellblaetter</normalizedToken>
gelb, 
<normalizedToken id="466EFA152EEAE6AE0197D8621684EF40" originalValue="glänzend" pageId="null" pageNumber="483">glaenzend</normalizedToken>
</emphasis>
, meist stumpf; 
<emphasis id="252F2DE70B3B51E5F8DE1ADA12E87B56" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="483">
die innern etwa doppelt so lang wie die 
<normalizedToken id="7BE82265368945833A01CCE638877082" originalValue="äußern" pageId="null" pageNumber="483">aeussern</normalizedToken>
.
</emphasis>
Frucht etwa 0,8 mm lang. 
<taxonomicName id="ACA86ACB7698A48656C6B189960023DC" class="Insecta" family="Miridae" genus="Pappus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hemiptera" pageId="null" pageNumber="483" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">Pappus</taxonomicName>
etwa 3 mm lang. - 
<normalizedToken id="832443957A42A8685B07688BCC5EBDE6" originalValue="Blüte" pageId="null" pageNumber="483">Bluete</normalizedToken>
: 
<normalizedToken id="944DB65FC16255DF5CC9FD032B366BE4" originalValue="Frühling" pageId="null" pageNumber="483">Fruehling</normalizedToken>
und Sommer.
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="3EC0DEC35370B49B478975B7E711608B" pageId="null" pageNumber="483">
<emphasis id="B88EB564E06898D06BC0BC86034A3019" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="483">Zytologische Angaben. 2n</emphasis>
= 
<emphasis id="F9EE887C1C91F9CCB2E6D86AD1ADC42B" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="483">28:</emphasis>
Material aus 
<normalizedToken id="DFD6139BC54045185785A3C91B809BE9" originalValue="Südwesteuropa" pageId="null" pageNumber="483">Suedwesteuropa</normalizedToken>
(Lorenzo-Andreu und Garcia-Sanz 1950, Gadella et al. 1966).
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="949CFA74C1B4D9B9A825DF2220BC4D44" pageId="null" pageNumber="483">
<emphasis id="280A44D6409EDB9DAB12BE509BA74478" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="483">Standort.</emphasis>
Kollin. Trockene, sandige und steinige 
<normalizedToken id="43905C3687FBDB587056D4E5E0148F06" originalValue="Böden" pageId="null" pageNumber="483">Boeden</normalizedToken>
in warmen Lagen. 
<normalizedToken id="127EF5736A4462AB7E5E9469FEF117CC" originalValue="Grasplätze" pageId="null" pageNumber="483">Grasplaetze</normalizedToken>
, Felsensteppen.
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="C97043A8F931527F0D25656C8FFA1A05" pageId="null" pageNumber="483">
<emphasis id="B357CB3C1B7D2348B2E5C2C764A1B942" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="483">
Verbreitung. 
<normalizedToken id="4DC62E8220738510BC9BA472F09A9CB3" originalValue="Südwesteuropäische" pageId="null" pageNumber="483">Suedwesteuropaeische</normalizedToken>
Pflanze:
</emphasis>
Iberische Halbinsel, 
<normalizedToken id="C96F57A34934907FABE9F5C7A58B244A" originalValue="Südfrankreich" pageId="null" pageNumber="483">Suedfrankreich</normalizedToken>
, Westseite der Apenninenhalbinsel. - Im Gebiet: 
<normalizedToken id="36F8759884F0B6B03B1EC929D8D24E96" originalValue="Dép" pageId="null" pageNumber="483">Dep</normalizedToken>
. Ain (Revermont, Bas Bugey), Savoyen (La Chambotte, Chignin).
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
